McLaren F1 GTR 
.
Shot by: @tshaxson 
.

The McLaren F1 GTR is a racing variant of the McLaren F1 sports car first produced in 1995 for grand touring style racing, such as the BPR Global GT Series, FIA GT Championship, JGTC, and British GT Championship. ... The F1 GTR raced internationally until 2005 when the final race chassis was retired.
